  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN THE COMMUNITY</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/0ce2abbc556c0a72efc1e27c3f0694a2.avif?t=1736176199\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><strong>Immerse yourself in an authentic atmosphere</strong> of Australian diverse biotopes set on the fire while exploring the Australian heritage sites and popular sightseeings!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/cb92112454db779ac41e11c107b505b7.poster.avif?t=1736176199\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/cb92112454db779ac41e11c107b505b7.webm?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/cb92112454db779ac41e11c107b505b7.mp4?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Drive through Australia as fast as possible<strong> to save endangered and endemic species</strong> by <strong>catching them into the nets</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/faf8a20c2285da486c38355d38ce4892.poster.avif?t=1736176199\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/faf8a20c2285da486c38355d38ce4892.webm?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/faf8a20c2285da486c38355d38ce4892.mp4?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Extinguishing fire</strong> is a critical skill to your survival and to the animals you indent to rescue. Fire is an obstacle on your way to animals to be rescued which spreads differently on a different level. <strong>Use water</strong> to free animals trapped in fire.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/4485b6bc2a474b5c138387a990a16c1d.poster.avif?t=1736176199\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/4485b6bc2a474b5c138387a990a16c1d.webm?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/4485b6bc2a474b5c138387a990a16c1d.mp4?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use bait when animals are hiding scared in burrows.<br><strong>Birds </strong>are also part of your rescue mission.<br>Finally, <strong>explore the lives of animals caught in the journal</strong>, including fun facts that you didn't know about.<br><br><i>PLEASE NOTE: We’re not working on the game anymore. As it goes in life, our way of living changed during the last months, and with that our priorities and goals as well. We have separated our ways and decided to go pursuits our own goals. During the development of this game, we learned so much and we hope you enjoyed the game as well. We really appreciate each one of you, and we want to thank you for your support. Some of us are still planning to create games so you may find yourself playing other games from some members of our team.</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/0ce2abbc556c0a72efc1e27c3f0694a2.avif?t=1736176199\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><strong>Immerse yourself in an authentic atmosphere</strong> of Australian diverse biotopes set on the fire while exploring the Australian heritage sites and popular sightseeings!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/cb92112454db779ac41e11c107b505b7.poster.avif?t=1736176199\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/cb92112454db779ac41e11c107b505b7.webm?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/cb92112454db779ac41e11c107b505b7.mp4?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Drive through Australia as fast as possible<strong> to save endangered and endemic species</strong> by <strong>catching them into the nets</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/faf8a20c2285da486c38355d38ce4892.poster.avif?t=1736176199\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/faf8a20c2285da486c38355d38ce4892.webm?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/faf8a20c2285da486c38355d38ce4892.mp4?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Extinguishing fire</strong> is a critical skill to your survival and to the animals you indent to rescue. Fire is an obstacle on your way to animals to be rescued which spreads differently on a different level. <strong>Use water</strong> to free animals trapped in fire.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/4485b6bc2a474b5c138387a990a16c1d.poster.avif?t=1736176199\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/4485b6bc2a474b5c138387a990a16c1d.webm?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510100/extras/4485b6bc2a474b5c138387a990a16c1d.mp4?t=1736176199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use bait when animals are hiding scared in burrows.<br><strong>Birds </strong>are also part of your rescue mission.<br>Finally, <strong>explore the lives of animals caught in the journal</strong>, including fun facts that you didn't know about.<br><br><i>PLEASE NOTE: We’re not working on the game anymore. As it goes in life, our way of living changed during the last months, and with that our priorities and goals as well. We have separated our ways and decided to go pursuits our own goals. During the development of this game, we learned so much and we hope you enjoyed the game as well. We really appreciate each one of you, and we want to thank you for your support. Some of us are still planning to create games so you may find yourself playing other games from some members of our team.</i>",
